Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes

What’s New for the Salesforce Release Notes?

How to Use the Release Notes

Get Ready for the Release

Monthly Release Notes

Release Update:

* Analytics: Report Formula Generation (Add calculated fields to your data cloud reports with Einstein Generative AI)
* Commerce: Semantic Search (Improve search results with Einstein semantic search)
* Industries: Education Cloud
  - Einstein Skills Generator (Use AI to set course and program expectations with Einstein skills generator)
  - Intelligent Question Generation (Draft questions by using Einstein for intake assessments)
  - Einstein Copilot: Fundraising Gift Proposals (Draft fundraising gift proposals with Einstein copilot, beta)
* June ’24: 
  - Analytics: Report Formula Generation
  - Field Service: Pre-Work Brief (Customize the pre-work brief with prompt builder)
  - Industries: Contracts: Contracts AI (Tailor your default and new field prompts for effective data extraction)
  - Industries: Health Cloud: Assessment Generation (Automate assessment generation with Einstein generative AI)
  - Industries: Net Zero Cloud: ESG Reports (Einstein for net zero cloud)
  - Overall: Salesforce Scheduler (Generate personalized appointment invitation emails with prompt builder)
  - Sales: Einstein Conversation Insights
  - Sales: Experience Cloud: Einstein Sales Emails for Partners (Help partners send personalized sales emails fast)
  - Service: Article Recommendations, Feedback Management, Work Summaries (Einstein for service)
  - Service: Service Catalog (Einstein for service catalog, beta)
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes
